Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了 ！\N辛苦了 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞节. . . 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,花菱薰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我打工完正要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,之前送去修理相机已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,对了，难得我碰在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要一起去吃个饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,走嘛，走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有相片给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有事情要处理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.44,0:00:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有机会再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯， 我知了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,改天见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这点钱没辨法外食啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:01:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然努力进了大学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,现实还真是严苛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不过，在离开花菱家时侯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我就已经有所觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.63,0:01:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,甚. . . 什么东西来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,请问...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在睡觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在睡觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,居然随便跑到大家家里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉 吓着你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我是圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚掉...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.71,0:02:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪？我刚刚明明就上锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，所以我就这个样子...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那么， 我重新自我介绍一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我是圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚我一个不注意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就把垂饰弄丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细一看 她好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,请问，有在听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是，垂饰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是，谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有这个东西的话\N就没辨法回到自己的国家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,弄丢时我相当困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,为了避免再弄丢 我得把它好好收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,样子就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,请问...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫花菱薰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,叫薰先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,薰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好回礼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我会没辨法释怀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不，真不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,薰先生想要东西是...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然她突然跟我话 她是圣诞老人...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她应该是人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不但温暖又很柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能和么可爱女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一起渡过圣诞节话...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对. . . 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我完全没有想过会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你知这是什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如. . . 如果不嫌弃我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那就一起度过圣诞节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那种事...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我虽然有过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不. . . 不过我是第一次做事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,应该怎么做才好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对了，我还没有问你名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不是，我是在问你名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,叫圣诞老人 我知了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可是样子有点难叫耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就叫我喜欢名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊，那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那么叫葵怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,葵. . . 真是固好名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是某个人名字吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一个跟我青梅竹马的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,小时侯常常玩在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非她是初恋女孩子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那样没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我有段时侯没见过她了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在完全不知她过得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,或许能够再度见到她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是薰先生的梦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我圣诞老人送给孩子礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是物品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而是让孩子在梦中梦见快乐的事，或是高兴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,梦...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然大部分孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在睡醒之后都会忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,即使时间短暂 但是如果能让他高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以也请想起快乐的事或是要见的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,想见的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此， 所以你才会要我这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，薰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因为今天是圣诞节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 一起来吃吧，薰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈 ！ 妈妈 ！ 妈妈 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:07:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀，薰真是爱撒娇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,男孩子怎么可以哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,薰先生在作着什么样梦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他应该是作着快乐梦才对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是为什么在哭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪？我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,原来我打完工后 就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪的梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,早. . . 安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看熏先生一脸谅讶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，你是圣诞老人  葵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,早餐已经做好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,原来那不是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞蛋糕跟火鸡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是圣诞老人 所以会做些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,（工屋游乐园）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,大家看起来好像都好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,心情好像也变得很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？薰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啦. . . 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,葵 你穿那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,身衣服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我很纳闷 为什么大家都不会觉得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,因为大家都不相信有圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不相信 大家就看不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,请不用跟我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为薰先生能够看得到我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，你走路看哪...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，你没有事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,撞到你真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,大姐 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,西园寺 ！跑到哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,害我找了好久呢 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快点，要走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是，大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女孩子也看得到葵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是，我不要紧...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,看来完全不是那么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,葵是第一次溜冰吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是，我是第一次溜冰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.96,0:09:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯. . 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,痛痛，痛痛，飞走吧 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不会痛了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哪， 不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,千夏， 你怎么了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉，真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,给您添麻烦了， 圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,路上心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,看得见葵 人蛮多嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在要参加签约会议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对没有在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,游乐园？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真是啊，在胡乱话些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真是有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得只有我么快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这样真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,让许多人在圣诞节感到快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是我使命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,偶然样也没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:12:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,让葵你自己来享受快乐...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我送你一个礼物 答谢你今天陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯， 你要什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要我为你做些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯. . . 这个嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没想过那事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我什么都不想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,葵...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,葵她...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一定得去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我要像这样 一直跟着她在一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,薰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这么快乐的圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你果然还是要去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.68,0:13:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,时间. . . 到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今年也要让孩子作快乐的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,希望今年也能有个好梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以薰先生那个时侯才会...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,人...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在起一生中最快乐事时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,原来会变得热泪盈眶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,葵...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,薰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我想到要什么礼物了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我会祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,希望有一天 薰先生能遇到真正的葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我会一直祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,薰先生，其实我...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得我好像睡了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我得快点门去打工才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪？是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕， 打工 ！ 打工 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
